sourcesContent: import React, { useContext } from 'react'; import { EventContext } from './EventContext'; import { Box, Container, Typography, Grid, Card, CardContent } from '@mui/material'; const StudentProfile = () => { const { events } = useContext(EventContext); // Show all events (no date filter) const allEvents = events; return ( 👤 Student Profile View your upcoming events 📅 Upcoming Events {allEvents.length === 0 ? ( No events available. ) : ( {[...allEvents].reverse().map((event) => ( 🎈 {event.name} {event.date ? new Date(event.date).toLocaleDateString() : ''} {event.location} Description: {event.description} ))} )} ); }; export default StudentProfile;
